query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('abstract-class',
'actions-on-google',
'arrays',
'hibernate',
'href',
'instance',
'jquery-validate',
'memory',
'mingw',
'navigation',
'reshape',
'rx-java',
'slider',
'subset')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Autobiographer',
'Census',
'Editor',
'Enlightened',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Famous Question',
'Nice Answer',
'Notable Question',
'Popular Question',
'Tumbleweed',
'Yearling')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
